Chicken With Tomatoes (Timitar Murghi)
?

2.5 tbsp vegetable oil
3/8 whole cumin seeds
1/2 inch cinnamon stick
3 whole cardamom pods
1 bay leaf
1/8 tsp black peppercorns
3+ cloves garlic
1 medium onion
1/2 inch cube ginger
3 medium tomatoes
1/2 lb chicken
3/4 tsp salt
less than 1/8 tsp cayenne pepper
1/4 tsp garam masala

Heat oil in a large wide pot over medium heat.  Put in cumin, cinnamon, cardamom, bay leaves and peppercorns.  Stir once.

Add onions, garlic, ginger until onions brown.

Put in peeled tomatoes, chicken, salt and cayenne.

Stir to mix, bring to a boil.

Cover, turn heat to low, simmer for 25 minutes.

Remove cover, turn heat to medium.  Add garam masala, cook for 5 minutes.  Whole spices not to eat.
